│ THOUGHT: The miscompilation in the reproducer is triggered by peeling within the LoopFullUnroll pipeline, which then miswires LCSSA and produces a more-undefined return value. A        │
│ targeted and non-invasive fix is to disable peeling specifically for LoopFullUnroll by setting the AllowPeeling argument to false in the LoopFullUnrollPass call to tryToUnrollLoop.     │
│ This avoids the problematic transformation without impacting other unroll paths. I will submit the patch for validation.                                                                 │
