│ THOUGHT: The reproducer miscompilation was caused by peeling within the LoopFullUnroll pipeline, which then miswired LCSSA. I implemented a targeted fix by disabling peeling            │
│ specifically when OnlyFullUnroll is true (setting AllowPeeling to false in LoopFullUnrollPass’s tryToUnrollLoop call). The reproducer now shows no incorrect transformation under        │
│ loop-unroll-full with max count 1. I will re-run the exact reproducer to confirm the output remains identical to the source.                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
